creator: Seedorsoft
descriptionHtml:
Seedor App

Bundles of applications for many business domains are available through the Seedor automation engine with a single user login.

Seedor People

It is Providing complete  HR solution for your business, Seedor people is built with rich feature set, end to end functional coverage starting from recruitment to retirement The attendance system that uses face recognition, geolocation, and geofencing. Employee timesheets can be tracked using Google Sheet Timecard, Quick Timesheets, and bulk group timesheet. 

Manage employee leaves, Keep track of all your employees’ vacations. Approve or refuse leave requests, Handle all requests from your employees. Create overtime request based on days and hours. These overtime could be utilize as leave allocation or cash payment.

Comprehensive payroll solution that’s fully integrated with other module.  Create your monthly employee gratuity sheet and create draft entry at the end of every month

Using letters can create a certificate like a certificate for appreciation, best employee of the month, experience certificate of our own

Calendars primarily support the setting of a specific date that is useful for scheduling meetings.

Seedor Affinity

Seedoraffinity (CRM) is a technique that allows businesses and other organizations to manage their connections with customers, Give your sales team the perfect set of apps to help close more business deals in less time.





Lead management, opportunity pipeline phases, and the wide spectrum of sales functions including inventory management are all provided by Affinity.

Seedor Project

Manage task with timesheets sales. team to send estimation to your customers for materials, labour, overheads details in Task estimation. 

Seedor Finance

Seedor Finance provides a well-established accounting platform with user friendly approach and advanced features to manage your financial operations. Seedor Accounting is integrated with Sales, Purchase and Expenses so manage all your transactions efficiently with full-fledged accounting reports.

Factory Seedor

Factory Seedor bundle helps manufacturers, warehouses and freight forwarders to automate their work flows efficiently. The integrated IOT applications makes the process even simpler, smarter and reliable.

Bill Seedor

Bill Seedor engages with retail business in a dynamic and integrated manner, be it a complex distribution business, or a hypermarket type or a single counter shop, bill Seedor can do the automation in no time.

Cafe Seedor

Café Seedor is tailored to support the hospitality industry, be it a simple or multi cuisine restaurant, or a multi star hotel, Cafe Seedor can make the entire work flow efficient, reliable and automated.

Edu Seedor

Edu Seedor is dedicated for learning, Entity Management System (EMS), Learning Management System (LMS) & Learning Management Toolkit (LMT)-(E-Learning, E-library, E-lab) are the segregation of this application bundle.

Build Seedor

Build Seedor makes construction industry more productive, MEP business, facade industry are the other businesses that can be benefited from the rich feature set of this bundle.
descriptionShort: The Seedor app provides a fully automated management solution for your business.
